            <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
            <meta property="og:image:height" content="1200">
            <meta property="og:image:alt" content="Textpattern logo">
        </txp:if_article_image>
        <script type="application/ld+json">
            {
                "@context": "https://schema.org",
                "@type": "WebPage",
                "headline": "<txp:title escape="json" />",
                "description": "<txp:meta_description format="" escape="json" />",
                "url": "<txp:permlink escape="json" />"
            }
        </script>
    </txp:if_article_list>
</head>
<body itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage">
    <txp:output_form form="body_header" />
    <main id="main" aria-label="Main content">
        <txp:if_article_list>
            <div class="container showcase-container showcase-landing">
                <txp:output_form form="body_crumbs" />
                <h1>Site showcase</h1>
                <img loading="lazy" class="showcase-rosette dark-contrast" width="132" height="200" alt="110% Awesome Websites" src="/assets/img/com/index-showcase.png" srcset="/assets/img/com/index-showcase@2x.png 2x">
                <div>
                    <p>Our users continue to amaze us with their wonderful creations! To suggest a website for consideration in our showcase please announce it within the forum <a href="https://forum.textpattern.com/viewforum.php?id=6">‘Showcase your Textpattern site’</a> section first—we then pick new showcase examples on an ad hoc basis.</p>
                </div>
                <section>
                    <h4 class="accessibility">List of site showcases</h4>
                    <txp:etc_cache id="landing-showcases">
                        <txp:article>
                            <article class="showcases" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article">
                                <a href="<txp:permlink />" aria-labelledby="headline_<txp:article_id />">
                                    <txp:images limit="1">
                                        <txp:smd_thumbnail type="showcase-teaser-318w212h">
                                            <span itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
                                                <picture>
                                                    <txp:output_form form="images_type" />
                                                    <img loading="lazy" class="img--showcase" width="318" height="212" alt="<txp:image_info type="alt" />" src="<txp:smd_thumbnail_info item="url" />" itemprop="url contentUrl">
                                                </picture>
                                                <meta itemprop="width" content="318">
                                                <meta itemprop="height" content="212">
                                            </span>
                                        </txp:smd_thumbnail>
                                    </txp:images>
                                </a>
                                <h4 id="headline_<txp:article_id />" itemprop="headline"><a itemprop="url mainEntityOfPage" href="<txp:permlink />" title="Full article"><txp:title /></a></h4>
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="The Textpattern Development Team">
                                <span itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization">
                                    <meta itemprop="name" content="Textpattern CMS">
                                    <span itemprop="logo" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
                                        <meta itemprop="url contentUrl" content="https://textpattern.com/assets/img/branding/textpattern/textpattern.png">
                                        <meta itemprop="width" content="320">
                                        <meta itemprop="height" content="60">
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="<txp:posted format="iso8601" />">
                                <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="<txp:modified format="iso8601" />">
                            </article>
                        </txp:article>
                    </txp:etc_cache>
                </section>
                <p class="alert-block information footnote"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Inclusion in this showcase is at the sole discretion of the The Textpattern Development Team. Any site may be removed at any time for any reason. The Textpattern Development Team is not directly responsible for any content or views expressed within third-party sites. See something wrong in this showcase? Please <a href="<txp:site_url />contact">contact us</a> and we’ll look into it.</p>
            </div>
        <txp:else />
            <div class="container">
                <div class="layout-container">
                    <txp:output_form form="body_crumbs" />
                    <article class="layout-4col-3span" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article">
                        <txp:article />
                        <p class="alert-block information footnote"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Inclusion in this showcase is at the sole discretion of the Textpattern Development Team. Any site may be removed at any time for any reason. The Textpattern Development Team is not directly responsible for any content or views expressed within third-party sites. See something wrong in this showcase? Please <a href="<txp:site_url />contact">contact us</a> and we’ll look into it.</p>
                    </article>
                    <txp:output_form form="sidebar" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </txp:if_article_list>
    </main>
    <txp:output_form form="body_footer" />
</body>
</html>
